texts.label: paragraph
texts.orig: Fedora 21 reached Alpha status last month and will  reach beta status  at the end of October. There are plenty of  new features planned  for the final release.
texts.text: Fedora 21 reached Alpha status last month and will  reach beta status  at the end of October. There are plenty of  new features planned  for the final release.

texts.label: paragraph
texts.orig: You can test Fedora 21 now using Rackspace's Cloud Servers. I've assembled a small Ansible playbook that will automate the upgrade process from Fedora 20 to 21 and it takes around 7-9 minutes to complete.
texts.text: You can test Fedora 21 now using Rackspace's Cloud Servers. I've assembled a small Ansible playbook that will automate the upgrade process from Fedora 20 to 21 and it takes around 7-9 minutes to complete.

texts.label: paragraph
texts.orig: The Ansible playbook is on GitHub along with instructions:  ansible-rax-fedora21
texts.text: The Ansible playbook is on GitHub along with instructions:  ansible-rax-fedora21
